commonMistakes.correction:
Forgetting to update the condition variable:
   let x = 0;
   while (x < 10) {
     console.log(x);  // x never changes - INFINITE LOOP!
   }

Updating in the wrong direction:
   let x = 0;
   while (x < 10) {
     console.log(x);
     x--;  // x gets MORE negative - INFINITE LOOP!
   }
